claim.claim-text:
1. A grill comprising:
a grill body, the grill body having an opening in a bottom portion of the grill body;
a burn box located directly below the grill body, the burn box having an open top end positioned under the opening in the bottom portion of the grill body;
a slide positioned to a side of the grill body and attached to the burn box for receiving burnable material which will be fed into the burn box by a slide.
